# Brain Tumor Segmentation using U-Net

This repository contains a Jupyter Notebook implementation of an AI-based
system for automatic brain tumor segmentation from MRI scans.

## Project Overview
The goal of this project is to support radiologists by automating the
segmentation of brain tumors using deep learning.

## Methodology
- Image preprocessing and enhancement
- Data augmentation
- U-Net architecture
- Evaluation using Dice Coefficient and IoU

## Tools & Technologies
- Python
- TensorFlow / Keras
- OpenCV
- NumPy

## Note
This project is for educational purposes only.
